### ============================================================================
### ADMIN → ANALYTICS / DASHBOARD — /api/v1/admin
### ============================================================================

### Dashboard stats
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/dashboard/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Analytics
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/analytics
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### AI logs
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/ai-logs?userId=&status=
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### AI log detail
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/ai-logs/{{aiRequestLogId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Flag AI log
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/ai-logs/{{aiRequestLogId}}/flag
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Admin plans list
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/plans?userId=&companyId=
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Admin plan detail
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/plans/{{planId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Flag plan
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/plans/{{planId}}/flag
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Archive plan
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/plans/{{planId}}/archive
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Delete plan (admin)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/plans/{{planId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Invoices list (admin billing)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/billing/invoices
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Invoice detail (admin billing)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/billing/invoices/{{invoiceId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Create invoice (admin billing)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/billing/invoices
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": {{userId}},
  "companyId": {{companyId}},
  "amount": 150000,
  "currency": "NGN",
  "description": "Monthly subscription"
}

### Update invoice (admin billing)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/billing/invoices/{{invoiceId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 200000,
  "description": "Updated monthly subscription"
}

### Mark invoice as paid
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/billing/invoices/{{invoiceId}}/paid
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
